ML Algorithm family => Classification and Regression

Liner =>
1. Liner => Liner regression (Regression)
         Logistic regression (Classification)

Non-liner =>
1. Tree-based => Decision tree
              Random forest

2. Distance-based => KNN
                  SVM

3. Ensemble => Random forest
            Gradient boosting


Logistic regression: Classification tasklar uchun ishlaydi. Sodda va kichik datasetlar uchun yaxshi ishlaydi.

Logistic Regression bosqichlari=> 
  Data preprocessing (cleaning, encoding, scaling)
  x, y (inputs(features) va outpu(target) ni aniqlash)
  splitting (train va test)
  Trainig(fitting)
  Predicting
  Evaluating

CODING:

```x=df.drop("target col name", axis=1)``` => inputlarni aniqlash
```y=df["target col name"]``` => outputni aniqlash

```from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split``` => train va test dataga ajratish uchun kutubxonadan funksiyani import qilish
```x_train,x_test,y_train,y_test=train_test_split(x, y, test_size=0.2, random_state=42)``` => import qilingan funksiyani ishlatish
```x_train.shape``` => ajratilgan data ni shaklini korish yani nechta ustun va qatordan iboratigini.


```from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression``` => Algorithmni import qilish
```log_reg=LogisticRegression()``` => log_reg ozgaruvchiga algorithmimizni olish.
```log_reg.fit(x_train, y_train)``` => train uchun ajratgan datamizni fitting qilish
```log_reg.predict(x_test)``` => test uchun ajratgan datamizni predict qilish

```from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score``` => Evaluation qilish uchun accuracy_score funksiyasini kutubxonadan import qilish
```accuracy_score(y_test, y_predict)``` => 0 va 1 oraligida qiymat qaytaradi bu qiymat accuracy score boladi.







